{"id": 1692, "genre": 1000, "title": "有哪些看起来是为别的年龄段提供的产品，你其实也很喜欢？", "description": "全年龄主义者的你都买过哪些跨年龄的产品？欢迎在评论区踊跃补充！（题图来自：Tasso Art）", "record_count": 10955, "comment_count": 66, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170516183935qc4X2EJrZTOmFPnC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-16T17:00:42Z", "questions": [{"id": 2340, "title": "有哪些看起来是为别的年龄段提供的产品，你其实也很喜欢？", "content": "有哪些为“专为“别的年龄段提供的产品，你其实也很喜欢？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 204302, "content": "那些专为小朋友写的百科真的很好看", "image": "img/option/option/20170516184625yGzKXu16I8B9Ew2b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204306, "content": "有的儿童玩具，超喜欢，也会为此买麦当劳儿童餐", "image": "img/option/option/20170516190107HC3XDiIAntb8NSsw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204307, "content": "因为个小脚小总要买童装童鞋，有的还挺好看", "image": "img/option/option/20170516190144NyELfXn5TZx4PVWs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204308, "content": "虽然还是青春年少，但未雨绸缪用抗衰老护肤品", "image": "img/option/option/20170516190214wlGnxb9OU4qAKYMd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204309, "content": "很多儿童零食都特好吃，我会时不时买", "image": "img/option/option/20170516190308tloHBr61w38JIV5T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204310, "content": "我是中老年表情的长期而真挚的爱好者", "image": "img/option/option/20170516221130NrRh9k3so8jlvuTM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204311, "content": "老人家用的按摩球和不求人啥的，简直是实用圣器", "image": "img/option/option/20170516190518FDIxMruUS6G5HapL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204312, "content": "有时候陪我妈跳广场舞，身心愉快", "image": "img/option/option/201705161912544TDfMRqE391yUPbp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}